    "reasoning": "I chose a muted moss-and-bark palette with warm parchment text to match Hollowmere’s eerie forest-folklore atmosphere. The accent and selection colors echo rowan wood, old ritual tokens, and weathered bronze, while the hover states stay slightly lighter for clear usability without breaking the somber tone. Dialogue and menu text are kept near-ivory for strong readability against dark, decayed backgrounds, and the disabled/muted colors are subdued green-gray tones that fit the setting while remaining distinct from active UI states."
